<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/../../css/mypage.css">
    <title>맡겨줘-내 정보</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("../header.ejs") %>
    <div id="body">
        <script>
            let openPop = function(){
                document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "block"
            }
            let closePop = function(){
                document.getElementById("popup").style.display = "none"
                document.getElementById("passwordInput").value = null;
            }
        </script>
        <%- include('menu.ejs') %>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>내 회원정보</h2>
            <ul class="userInfo">
                <b>아이디</b>
                <li><%= user.id %></li>
                <b>이름</b>
                <li><%= user.name %></li>
                <b>이메일</b>
                <li><%= user.email %></li>
                <button id="modiButton" onclick="openPop()">회원정보 수정하기</button>
            </ul>
            <div id="popup">
                <div id="passwordChk">
                    <h2>회원정보 수정</h2>
                    <p>
                        본인확인을 위해 비밀번호를 입력해주세요.
                    </p>
                    <form method="post">
                        비밀번호 <input type="password" name="password">
                        <button type="submit">확인</button>
                    </form>
                    <br>
                    <button onclick="closePop()">닫기</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>